{
  "id": "5c47d74495f9e3001710f060",
  "title": "正のフィードバック",
  "created": 1548212357,
  "updated": 1564298340,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c47d74495f9e3001710f060",
      "text": "正のフィードバック",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212357,
      "updated": 1548212357
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d885aff09e00003bc01a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/03f405e98bc95b76c2bb4b9478275ec7]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212357,
      "updated": 1548212363
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d88aaff09e0000f218cc",
      "text": "\tどんどん大きくなるし、増加速度が加速する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212363,
      "updated": 1548212541
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d8b6aff09e00003bc01b",
      "text": "\t[ポジティブフィードバック]ともいう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212407,
      "updated": 1548212463
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d8efaff09e00003bc01c",
      "text": "\t\tコミュニケーションにおける「肯定的なフィードバック」と混同しないように注意",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212464,
      "updated": 1548212480
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d900aff09e00003bc01d",
      "text": "\t右図、どんどん小さくなり、減る速度が加速するケースも「ポジティブフィードバック」である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212480,
      "updated": 1548212553
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d924aff09e00003bc01e",
      "text": "\t\t「ポジティブ」という言葉の雰囲気のせいで勘違いされがち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212517,
      "updated": 1548212554
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d98baff09e00003bc01f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212619,
      "updated": 1548212620
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d88aaff09e0000f218cb",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/db33a4fd706b1f0f7fe883f73726586d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212363,
      "updated": 1548212596
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d974aff09e0000f218ce",
      "text": "\t値が基準値からずれているときに、そのずれを拡大する(=ずれの向きと同じ方向の、ポジティブな）力がかかる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212596,
      "updated": 1548212689
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47d974aff09e0000f218cd",
      "text": "\tだから「増える方向にどんどん加速する」のも「減る方向にどんどん加速する」のもポジティブフィードバック",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212596,
      "updated": 1548212722
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47da14aff09e00003bc022",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212757,
      "updated": 1548212761
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47da19aff09e00003bc023",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/47b5c3920983a64495cd9dc8c6f9b9cf]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212762,
      "updated": 1548212816
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47da4faff09e0000f218cf",
      "text": "\t[ネガティブフィードバック]とは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212816,
      "updated": 1548213045
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47da79aff09e00003bc024",
      "text": "\t逆に、基準値からずれた時に、そのずれを縮小する方向に力がかかる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212857,
      "updated": 1548212857
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47da86aff09e00003bc025",
      "text": "\tだから、外乱などでずれた後、そのずれが減って元の基準値に戻る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212870,
      "updated": 1548212903
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47daa6aff09e00003bc027",
      "text": "\tつまりネガティブフィードバックは[安定]をもたらす",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212903,
      "updated": 1548212998
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47da9caff09e00003bc026",
      "text": "\tネガティブという言葉のせいで悪いものだという勘違いをする人がいるが、善悪に対応するものではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548212892,
      "updated": 1548213090
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47db62aff09e00003bc029",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213090,
      "updated": 1548213090
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47db62aff09e00003bc02a",
      "text": "\t[正帰還]・[負帰還]ともいう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213090,
      "updated": 1548213108
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47db73aff09e00003bc02b",
      "text": "\t[ハウリング]は[ポジティブフィードバック]の例。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213108,
      "updated": 1548213240
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47dbf8aff09e00003bc02c",
      "text": "\t\tマイクから入った音が拡大されてスピーカーから出て、それがまたマイクに拾われることで大音響に発展する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213240,
      "updated": 1548213240
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47db11aff09e00003bc028",
      "text": "\t我々の身の回りの安定しているものには、何らかの形でネガティブフィードバックが関わっている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213009,
      "updated": 1548213319
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47dc47aff09e00003bc02e",
      "text": "\t\t例えば体温",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213319,
      "updated": 1548213326
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47dc4eaff09e00003bc02f",
      "text": "\t\t\t体温が上がると、体表に汗を出して気化熱で冷却し、温度を下げようとする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213326,
      "updated": 1548213374
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47dc60aff09e00003bc030",
      "text": "\t\t\t体温が下がると、筋肉を震えさせて熱を生み出し、温度を上げようとする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213344,
      "updated": 1548213379
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47dc37aff09e00003bc02d",
      "text": "\t\t[ホメオスタシス]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213304,
      "updated": 1548213386
    },
    {
      "id": "5c47dc86aff09e00003bc031",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548213383,
      "updated": 1548213383
    },
    {
      "id": "5d3d4c5baff09e0000b66bca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1564298332,
      "updated": 1564298332
    },
    {
      "id": "5d3d4c5baff09e0000b66bcb",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1564298332,
      "updated": 1564298333
    },
    {
      "id": "5d3d4c5daff09e0000b66bcd",
      "text": "\t[エコーチェンバー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1564298333,
      "updated": 1564298340
    },
    {
      "id": "5d3d4c5daff09e0000b66bcc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1564298333,
      "updated": 1564298333
    }
  ]
}